  "title": "Wealth Manager",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Summary</strong></u></p>\n<p>Provide comprehensive wealth management services to high-net-worth individuals, families, and institutions, helping them achieve their financial goals and objectives.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Client Relationship Management: Build and maintain strong relationships with clients, understanding their financial goals, risk tolerance, and expectations.</p>\n<p>2. Financial Planning: Develop and implement comprehensive financial plans, including investment, tax, estate, and retirement planning.</p>\n<p>3. Investment Management: Manage client investment portfolios, including asset allocation, security selection, and portfolio rebalancing.</p>\n<p>4. Wealth Protection: Provide guidance on wealth protection strategies, including insurance, estate planning, and asset protection.</p>\n<p>5. Retirement Planning: Help clients plan for retirement, including creating sustainable income streams and optimizing retirement accounts.</p>",
